  "detailed_description": "<strong>Use, edit and organize monsters</strong> on a game grid to create a path to send the appropriate cans to the cute bat monster. Be sure not to make mistakes, he has a temper.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917900/extras/fa626ca148c042f36046bf42d5ca105e.poster.avif?t=1607273616\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917900/extras/fa626ca148c042f36046bf42d5ca105e.webm?t=1607273616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/917900/extras/fa626ca148c042f36046bf42d5ca105e.mp4?t=1607273616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Based on esoteric programming languages Befunge and Trefunge<br></li><li> 42 unique levels<br></li><li> 7 Hand-drawn biomes<br></li><li> 13 different monsters<br></li><li> Harder Dark World levels<br></li><li> Compete online with your friends, the world and even the dev!</li></ul>",
